---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Our privacy practices: no personal data collection, no cookies, no tracking. We use Plausible for anonymous, aggregate analytics."
>
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:text-heading prose-p:text-foreground prose-li:text-foreground prose-a:text-primary prose-strong:text-heading prose-ul:text-foreground">
        <h1>Privacy</h1>

        <p>The short version: we don't collect your personal data. No accounts, no email signups, no forms.</p>

        <h2>Analytics</h2>

        <p>This site uses <a href="https://plausible.io" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Plausible</a>, a privacy-focused analytics tool. Plausible doesn't use cookies, doesn't track you across sites, and doesn't collect personal information. We see aggregate numbers — page views, referral sources, country-level location — not individual visitors. Plausible is GDPR-compliant without requiring consent banners because it doesn't process personal data.</p>

        <h2>What we don't do</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>No email collection</li>
          <li>No user accounts</li>
          <li>No contact forms storing data</li>
          <li>No advertising or tracking pixels</li>
          <li>No data sold or shared with third parties</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If this changes, we'll update this page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
